Introduction

Welcome to King Plus VPN, a VPN (Virtual Private Network) application developed by [Your Company Name]. At King Plus VPN, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our VPN application.

1. Information We Collect

1.1. Android ID: King Plus VPN collects your Android device's unique identifier, known as the Android ID. We use this information to provide you with our VPN services and to improve your user experience. Please note that we do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) such as your name, email address, or browsing history.

2. How We Use Your Information

2.1. VPN Services: We use your Android ID to deliver and maintain our VPN services, including connecting you to our servers and optimizing your connection.

2.2. Improvement of Services: We may analyze aggregated, non-personal data to enhance the performance, features, and security of our application.

3. Data Security

3.1. Data Encryption: We prioritize your data security. All data transmitted between your device and our servers is encrypted to protect it from unauthorized access.

3.2. No Logging: We have a strict no-logs policy. We do not log or store any information related to your online activities, including your browsing history, IP address, or the content of your internet traffic.

4. Information Sharing

4.1. Third Parties: We do not share your Android ID or any other data with third parties for marketing or advertising purposes.

4.2. Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or when we believe such disclosure is necessary to protect our rights, legal interests, or comply with a legal process.

5. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. Any changes will be posted on our website and, where appropriate, notified to you via the application.

6. Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or the use of your data, please contact us 

7. Consent

By using King Plus VPN, you consent to the collection and use of your Android ID as described in this Privacy Policy.

Thank you for choosing King Plus VPN. Your privacy and security are of utmost importance to us.
